headline: 3 Accident & Health Insurance Stocks to Watch Amid Pricing Pressure
summary: Accident and Health Insurance stocks like AFL, TRUP and GL are set to gain from rising underwriting exposure and accelerated digitalization. However, pricing pressure is a concern given rising medical costs and inflation.
